cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper discusses a method for training linear SVMs for various recognition systems, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). The focus on large-scale learning and out-of-core datasets also suggests that the paper may be relevant to the sub-categories of databases (cs.DB) and information retrieval (cs.IR). However, given the specific applications mentioned in the abstract, the first five categories listed are the most likely.
